{"id":741462,"date":[{"year":1987,"month":1,"day":29}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"184","ytitle":"","mtitle":"嫩绿","ftitle":"","authors":["钱国梁"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱国梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老树爆一枝嫩绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一枝春阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一枝春雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻盈盈水灵灵，似云如玉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才是开春的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上还留有残雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫩绿，挤碎冬的压抑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很好!我的老树深深扎进泥土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然是盘根错节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有自然的凋谢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫩绿是新的生命的开始，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是新的希望的序曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象初生的婴儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象初恋的窈窕少女。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生机总凭着绿色的力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起一个万木葱茏的季节。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的小院不再荒芜了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿我的心里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多一些嫩绿，多一些春意。"}]}